
Release History
---------------------------------

Legend:
+ Added feature
* Improved/changed feature
- Bug fixed
! Known issue / missing feature



---------------------------------
Version 2.0.0 - Jan 9, 2015
---------------------------------

+ added Google Analytics tracking code support
* removed protocol prefix in templates to support http/https

=> make sure to update your config.ini.

---------------------------------
Version 1.9.0 - Sep 26, 2014
---------------------------------

* minor code cleanup
+ added reply link based on message id (msgId)

---------------------------------
Version 1.8.3 - Dec 09, 2012
---------------------------------

* minor code cleanup

---------------------------------
Version 1.8.2 - Oct 11, 2012
---------------------------------

+ added support to display correct context (admin|send)
* improved translations
* improved form styling

---------------------------------
Version 1.8.1 - Oct 09, 2012
---------------------------------

+ added language switcher in form.php
* improved translations
* improved form styling
* lowered default perturbation for CAPTCHAs in form
- fixed wrong argument counts in printForm

---------------------------------
Version 1.8.0 - Sep 17, 2012
---------------------------------

+ added file attachments
+ added locale and translations for en_US and de_AT (more translations are welcome :) )

---------------------------------
Version 1.7.3 - Aug 18, 2012
---------------------------------

+ released on GitHub
* minor code improvements

---------------------------------
Version 1.7.2 - Jun 06, 2012
---------------------------------

+ added error log
- removed copyright notice in footer

---------------------------------
Version 1.7.1 - Nov 25, 2010
---------------------------------

- fixed warning when no list was specified

---------------------------------
Version 1.7 - Oct 18, 2010
---------------------------------

+ added support for customizeable form, member and error file for mailing lists
* optimized file reading of members file
* updated config.ini

---------------------------------
Version 1.6 - Oct 17, 2010
---------------------------------

* updated CSS and HTML
- fixed escaping of quotation character in messages
- fixed bug in returning members list when members file was empty

---------------------------------
Version 1.5 - Oct 06, 2010
---------------------------------

+ added option to notify admin email in case of member updates
+ lists are now in seperate folders under the lists-root folder for easier
  management
+ added automatic generation of .htaccess file for lists-root folder
* optimized functions (added add, remove members)
* file entries are now identified by unique hashes
* updated form.php, members.php and error.php
* updated README

---------------------------------
Version 1.4 - Oct 05, 2010
---------------------------------

+ created error.php
+ created style.css
* using absolute path for the reason of optimization
* form now retains data on error
* fixed sending via BCC
* updated README

---------------------------------
Version 1.3 - Oct 02, 2010
---------------------------------

+ added captcha support for anti-spam protection
* updated form
* converted to class

---------------------------------
Version 1.2 - Sep 30, 2010
---------------------------------

+ added swiftmailer for sending mails
+ added configuration library
+ removed domain from email in member list
+ list members are now BCC when sending mail
* fixed warnings in form.php
* updated layout of form.php
* switched to plaintext email

---------------------------------
Version 1.1 - Sep 25, 2010
---------------------------------

+ added authorization mechanism for joining a list
+ added members list
* updated form.php

---------------------------------
Version 1.0 - Sep 22, 2010
---------------------------------

+ initial release
